# AN AUTOMATED INTENT ROUTING AND SCIENTIFIC TRUST FRAMEWORK FOR HIGH-CADENCE TRANSIT AND MICROLENSING DISCOVERIES WITHIN THE ROMAN GALACTIC BULGE SURVEY

Sierra Warren  
Stellar Intelligence Consortium  
ORCID: 0009-0004-2368-6030

